<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="413" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,402,1758]" pageId="12" pageNumber="413">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,333,1699,1723]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="413" reason="1">Etymology.</emphasis>
This specific name is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[887,1000,1699,1723]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="413">extumidus</emphasis>
(= projecting), referring to the large triangular projection at distal 1/4 of the costa.
</paragraph>
